"Puppy Patrol": A group of flying dogs trained to act as search and rescue dogs, able to reach areas inaccessible to ground-based dogs.
"Canine Airways": A dog airline where dogs can fly with their owners, offering pet-friendly cabins and in-flight services.
"Doggy Delivery": A delivery service where dogs can fly packages to their destinations, making deliveries faster and more efficient.
"Flying Fido": A dog-themed amusement park featuring dog flying demonstrations and interactive dog flying exhibits.
"Pupper Paws": A dog flying adventure game where players control flying dogs on aerial missions, collecting treats and avoiding obstacles.
